hadiths[16]{hadithnumber,text}:
2410,"maine aik shakhs ko Quran ki aayat is tarah padhtey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maine iske khilaf suna tha. isliye main unka hath thaamey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (meraa aetraz sun kar) farmaya ke tum donon durust ho. Shoba ne bayan kya ke main samajhta hun ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye bhi farmaya ke ikhtilaf na karo, kyonke tum se pahley log ikhtilaf hi ki wjah se tabah ho gaey."
2411,"2 logon ne jin mein aik musalman tha aur doosra yahoodii, aik doosrey ko bura-bhala kaha, musalman ne kaha, us zaat ki qasam! jisne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tamam duniya walon par buzurgi di aur Yahudi ne kaha, us zaat ki qism jisne Musa (Alaihissalam) ko tamam duniya walon par buzurgi di. is par musalman ne hath utha kar Yahudi ke tamaancha maaraa. wo Yahudi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur musalman ke sath apne waqia ko bayan kya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us musalman ko bulaya aur us se waaqie ke mutaalliq poochha. unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski tafseel bata di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske baad farmaya, mujhey Musa (Alaihissalam) par tarjeeh na do. log qiyamat ke din behosh kar diye jaengey. main bhi behosh ho jaaunga. be-hoshi se hosh mein aaney wala sabse pahlaa shakhs main hoonga, lekin Musa (Alaihissalam) ko arshe-Ilaahii ka kinara pakdey huey paaunga. ab mujhey malum nahi ke Musa (Alaihissalam) bhi behosh honey walon mein hongey aur mujh se pahley unhein hosh aa jaeyga ya Allah Taala ne unko un logon mein rakha hai jo behoshii se mustashnaa hain."
2412,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif farma they ke aik Yahudi aaya aur kaha ke aey abul-Qaasim! aap ke ashaab mein se aik ne mujhey tamaancha maara hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, kis ne? usne kaha ke aik Ansari ne. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein bulaao. wo aaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya tum ne usey maara hai? unhon-ne kaha ke maine usey bazar mein ye qism khaatey suna. us zaat ki qasam! jisne Musa (Alaihissalam) ko tamam insanon par buzurgi di. maine kaha, O, khabees! kya Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par bhi! mujhey ghussa aaya aur maine iske munh par thappad de maaraa. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya dekho anbiya mein aapasii aik doosrey par is tarah buzurgi na diya karo. log qiyamat mein behosh ho jaengey. apni qabr se sabse pahley nikalney wala main hi hoonga. lekin main dekhoonga ke Musa (Alaihissalam) arshe-Ilaahii ka paaya pakdey huey hain. ab mujhey malum nahi ke Musa (Alaihissalam) bhi behosh hongey aur mujh se pahley hosh mein aa jaeinge ya unhein pehli be-hoshii jo taur par ho chuki hai wahi kafi hogi."
2413,"aik Yahudi ne aik ladki ka sar 2 pattharon ke darmyan rakh kar kuchal diya tha. (is mein kuchh jaan baqi thi) us se puchha gaya ke terey sath ye kis ne kya hai? kya falan ne, falan ne? jab us Yahudi ka naam aaya to usne apne sar se ishara kya (ke haan) Yahudi pakda gaya aur usne bhi jurm ka iqrar kar liya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya aur uska sar bhi 2 pattharon ke darmyan rakh kar kuchal diya gaya."
2414,aik sahabi koi cheez khareedtey waqt dhokaa kha jaya kartey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke jab to khareedaa karey to ye keh de ke koi dhokaa na ho. to wo isi tarah kaha kartey they.
2415,"aik shakhs ne apna aik ghulam aazad kya, lekin uske paas iske siwa aur koi maal na tha. isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey iska ghulam wapas kara diya aur usey Naeem-bin-Nahaam ne khareed liya."
2416,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jisne koi jhooti qism jaan-boojh kar khaaii taake kisi musalman ka maal naajaaiz taur par hasil kar ley. to wo Allah Taala ke samney us haalat mein hazir hoga ke Allah paak is par bahut hi ghazabnaak hoga. rawi ne bayan kya ke is par Ashas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ki qasam! mujh se hi mutaalliq aik masley mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya tha. mere aur aik Yahudi ke darmyan aik zameen ka jhagdaa tha. us ne inkar kya to maine muqaddima Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se malum farmaya, kya tumharey paas koi gawah hai? maine kaha ke nahi. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Yahudi se farmaya ke phir to qism khaa. Ashas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya, ya Rasulullah! phir to ye jhooti qism kha lega aur mera maal uda ley jaeyga is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا ( '' beshak wo log jo Allah ke ahad aur apni qasmon se thodi poonchii khareedtey hain.'' aakhir aayat tak."
2417,"rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jisne koi jhooti qism jaan-boojh kar khaaii taake kisi musalman ka maal naajaaiz taur par hasil kar ley. to wo Allah Taala ke samney us haalat mein hazir hoga ke Allah paak is par bahut hi ghazabnaak hoga. rawi ne bayan kya ke is par Ashas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ki qasam! mujh se hi mutaalliq aik masley mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya tha. mere aur aik Yahudi ke darmyan aik zameen ka jhagdaa tha. us ne inkar kya to maine muqaddima Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se malum farmaya, kya tumharey paas koi gawah hai? maine kaha ke nahi. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Yahudi se farmaya ke phir to qism khaa. Ashas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya, ya Rasulullah! phir to ye jhooti qism kha lega aur mera maal uda ley jaeyga is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا ( '' beshak wo log jo Allah ke ahad aur apni qasmon se thodi poonchii khareedtey hain.'' aakhir aayat tak."
2418,"unhon-ne ibne- abii-Hadrad (Raziallahu anhu) se masjid main apne qarz ka taqaza kya aur donon ki awaz itni buland ho gaee ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi ghar mein sun li. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hujra Mubarak ka parda utha kar pukara aey Kab! unhon-ne arz kya, ya Rasulullah main hazir hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne qarz mein se itna kam kar de aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aadha qarz kam kar dene ka ishara kya. unhon-ne kaha ke maine kam kar diya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ibne- abii-Hadrad (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke uth ab qarz ada kar de."
2419,"maine Hishaam-bin-Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) ko sura furqan aik baar us qirat se padhtey suna jo iske khilaf thi jo main padhta tha. halanke meri qirat khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey sikhai thi. qareeb tha ke main fauran hi un par kuchh kar baithoon, lekin maine unhein mohlat di ke wo (namaz se) farigh ho lein. iske baad maine unke galley mein chadar daal kar unko ghaseetaa aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir kya. maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke maine unhein us qirat ke khilaf padhtey suna hai jo aap ne mujhey sikhai hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ke pahley unhein chhod de. phir unse farmaya ke achchha ab tum qirat sunao. unhon-ne wahi apni qirat sunai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke isi tarah nazil hui thi. iske baad mujh se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ab tum bhi padho, maine bhi padh kar sunaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke isi tarah nazil hui. Quran saat (7) qiraton mein nazil hua hai. tum ko jis mein aasani ho isi tarah se padh liya karo."
2420,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, maine to ye irada kar liya tha ke Namaz ki jamat qaaim karne ka hukm de kar khud un logon ke gharon mein jaun jo jamat mein hazir nahi hotey aur unke ghar ko jalaa dun."
2421,Zam-aa ki aik baandi ke ladey ke barey mein abd-bin Zam-aa (Raziallahu anhu) aur Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) apna jhagdaa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein lekar gaey. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah! mere bhai ne mujh ko wasiiyat ki thi ke jab main (Makka) aaoon aur Zam-aa ki baandi ke ladkey ko dekhun to usey apni parwarish mein ley loon. kyonke wo unhein ka ladka hai. aur abd-bin-Zam'a ne kaha ke wo mera bhai hai aur mere bap ki baandi ka ladka hai. mere walid hi ke ''faraash'' main uski paidaaish hui hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bachchey ke andar ( Utba ki) waazeh mushabihat (similarity) dekhi. lekin farmaya ke aey Abd-bin-Zam'a! ladka to tumhari hi parwarish mein rahega kyonke ladkaa'' faraash'' ke taabea' hota hai aur Sauda to us ladkey se parda kya kar.
2422,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chand sawaaron ka aik lashkar Najad ki taraf bhejaa. ye log banu-Haneefa ke aik shakhs ko jiska naam Samaama-bin-Assaal tha aur jo ahale-Yamaama ka sardaar tha, pakad laey aur usey masjide-Nabawi ke aik sutoon mein baandh diya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne poochha, samaama! to kis khayal mein hai? unhon-ne kaha aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mein achchha hun. phir unhon-ne poori hadis zikr ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke Samama ko chhod do."
2423,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sawaaron ka aik lashkar Najad ki taraf bheja jo banu-Haneefa ke aik shakhs Samaama-bin-Assaal ko pakad laey aur masjid ke aik sutoon se usko baandh diya.
2424,"Abdullah-bin abii-Hadrad Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) par unka qarz tha, unse mulaqat hui to unhon-ne unka peechhaa kya. phir donon ki guftgu tez honey lagi aur awaz buland ho gaee. itney main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka idhar se guzar hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey Kab! aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se ishara karke maano ye farmaya ke aadhey qarz ki kami kar de. chunanche unhon-ne aadha ley liya aur aadha qarz maaf kar diya."
2425,"main jahiliyat ke zamane mein lohey ka kaam karta tha aur Aas-bin-Waail (kaafir) par mere kuchh rupye qarz they. main uske paas taqaza karne gaya to usne mujh se kaha ke jab tak to Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka inkar nahi karega main tera qarz ada nahi karunga. maine kaha hargiz nahi, Allah ki qasam! mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka inkar kabhi nahi kar sakta, yahan tak ke Allah Taala tumhen maarey aur phir tum ko uthaaey. wo kehney laga ke phir mujh se bhi taqaza na kar. main jab mar ke dobara zinda hunga to mujhey (doosri zindagi mein) maal aur aulad di jaeygi to tumhara qarz bhi ada kar doonga. is par ye aayat nazil huii ( أفرأيت الذي كفر بآياتنا وقال لأوتين مالا وولدا‏ ) ''tum ne us shakhs ko dekha jisne hamari aayaton ka inkar kya aur kaha ke mujhey maal aur aulad zaroor di jaaeygii.'' aakhir aayat tak."
